title: 服务器某名奇妙的掉tps
author: ZacharyAlexa
txt_content:
本帖最后由 skyliye 于 2020-5-31 17:58 编辑 

 版本1.15.2（在线6个人，tps1m就9.71）
下面是stop之后的报错
[21:01:59 ERROR]: ------------------------------
[21:01:59 ERROR]: The server has stopped responding! This is (probably) not a Paper bug.
[21:01:59 ERROR]: If you see a plugin in the Server thread dump below, then please report it to that author
[21:01:59 ERROR]:        *Especially* if it looks like HTTP or MySQL operations are occurring
[21:01:59 ERROR]: If you see a world save or edit, then it means you did far more than your server can handle at once
[21:01:59 ERROR]:        If this is the case, consider increasing timeout-time in spigot.yml but note that this will replace the crash with LARGE lag spikes
[21:01:59 ERROR]: If you are unsure or still think this is a Paper bug, please report this to https://github.com/PaperMC/Paper/issues
